game.name: Oil Wrestling
game.description:
Like many others, you look pretty excited to explore the amazing world of action packed arenas. Well, luckily we have brought to you a brand new action game where you will have a plenty of opportunities to show off your ultimate fighting moves. Yes, we are talking about Oil Wresting, which you will have to wrestle with the most aggressive and powerful opponents. Don’t need to show pity on them until you have got the success in knocking the other player to the floor!

The controls are pretty simple in this two players fighting game that is also combined with the amazing graphics and cool sound. Give your opponents a solid response by making forward, left and right lunges! Available in five total levels, this one of the best wresting games allows those players who do score five first win the trophy. Apply the best possible wresting moves to be the master of this cool wrester game! Choose from single or two player mode while exploring it in your device!

Destroy objects and learn quickly how to deal with your opponents to become an oil wresting champion in this physics-based wrestling game! It’s up to you - play 3D wresting either with a friend or an AI controlled opponent! Join this latest fighting challenge to wear a crown of a mini wresting tournament on your desktop, mobile phone or tablet! The smooth movement combined by the 3D graphics and funny sounds and music will keep you entertained for hours. Give our more action gams a try to create goosebumps in your body!
